Class Candle

  • java.lang.Object
    • stocker.util.Candle
  • public class Candle
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a Candle for use in a candlestick chart. Pure data container with public attributes.

    • Constructor Detail

      • Candle

        public Candle​(long t,
              double l,
              double h,
              double o,
              double c,
              double v)
        Constructs a new Candle from the values given as parameters.
        Parameters:
        t - The unix timestamp of this candle (type long)
        l - The lowest price during this candle's interval (type double)
        h - The highest price during this candle's interval (type double)
        o - The opening price, at the beginning of this candle's interval (type double)
        c - The closing price, at the end of this candle's interval (type double)
        v - The volume of trading for this candle (type double)
